Indigo Valley Farm

A Jersey Fresh Regenerative Farm

Who We Are

Indigo Valley Farm is a regenerative agricultural operation committed to cultivating ethnically important crops, culinary and medicinal herbs, and artisanal delicacies. As beginner farmers, we blend ancient wisdom with modern technology to produce highly delicious and nutritious produce.

Our farm family upholds the highest standards of quality, safety, environmental stewardship, and cultural responsibility. We believe in healing together, from soil to soul, creating a new kind of community rooted in the Ubuntu philosophy.

"I am what I am because of who we all are."
